title: Jar And Cover, ca. 1830
dimensions: H x diam.: 33 x 11.8 cm (13 x 4 5/8 in.)
description: Slender urn-shaped body cut with shallow diamond pattern all over, a row ofthin fluting at top edge, wide flutes at base; fluted stem on square base cut with star on bottom; tall bell-shaped cover cut with shallow diamond pattern and prismatic rings, faceted finial.

tombstone.epitaph:
Jar And Cover, ca. 1830.
ca. 1830. glass. Bequest of Walter Phelps Warren. 1986-61-95-a,b.
